  "3282520": {
    "name": "花园与鸟",
    "steam_appid": 3282520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让我们和小鸟们一起，改造荒岛吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小鸟带来了植物和装饰品，将荒岛变成属于你自己的独特花园。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在这个花园里我们有——</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过30种<strong>「小鸟」</strong>为你带来礼物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种下种子收集超过150种<strong>「植物」</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买超过400种<strong>「装饰品」</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过60个<strong>「小精灵」</strong>和<strong>「专属小屋」</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有任务，只有纯粹的<strong>「自由」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/82af2c55076b23e157abbeb0e312a21d.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/82af2c55076b23e157abbeb0e312a21d.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/82af2c55076b23e157abbeb0e312a21d.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小鸟带来了什么？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你可能得到种子、礼物，或者……鸟屎？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不论是什么，都可以成为花园的一部分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把它们放到地面上，等待种子生长或者拆开礼物……然后自由地摆放它们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3b736e3ea173a8502634eb635870115a.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3b736e3ea173a8502634eb635870115a.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3b736e3ea173a8502634eb635870115a.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不知名的种子</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是什么种子呢？一朵花，一棵树，或者是一个蘑菇！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >植物千奇百怪，也许有些你并不喜欢。没关系，卖掉它们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好吧，植物也许不会伤心，但是制作它的我们会;_;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3159b2bdba35921bac9f4fd9e465db21.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3159b2bdba35921bac9f4fd9e465db21.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/3159b2bdba35921bac9f4fd9e465db21.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神奇的箱子</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>总之，这个箱子可以把所有东西都变成星星币。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个箱子链接着另一个国度，只要你把东西放进去，它们就会变成货币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哦，小精灵不行，他们不喜欢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/aab9c3ceb28ed4108d33dadbb1aa486c.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/aab9c3ceb28ed4108d33dadbb1aa486c.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/aab9c3ceb28ed4108d33dadbb1aa486c.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小精灵和它的岛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>箱子上的小鸟可以回收星星币，也就是它会卖东西。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么小鸟会卖东西？为什么小鸟有异次元背包？为什么背包里有小精灵？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别问那么多为什么，把小精灵买下来就对了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/cbc64108ff6c68f683d20a70be6bcd2f.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/cbc64108ff6c68f683d20a70be6bcd2f.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/cbc64108ff6c68f683d20a70be6bcd2f.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >享受这一切</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这里没有任务，没有感叹号，没有最终boss……你是自由的！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许这和你平时玩的游戏不太一样，你必须自己决定该干什么！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以只为了全收集，也可以自己设定一个主题进行创作，或者盯着鸟发呆……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/93f2e15c785ed4889d02e101d9245278.poster.avif?t=1763889793\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/93f2e15c785ed4889d02e101d9245278.webm?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282520/extras/93f2e15c785ed4889d02e101d9245278.mp4?t=1763889793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >联系我们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><a href=\"mailto:email：982445535@qq.com\">email：982445535@qq.com</a></strong></p>",
